        "code": "HTML-1775422942644",
        "type": "HTML",
        "description": "simulator_health",
        "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"fr\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes\">\n    <title>🏥 Simulateur Capteurs Santé - IoT Médical</title>\n\t$content(STYLE-1775422961591)\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <h1>🏥 Capteurs Santé IoT</h1>\n            <p>Simulateur de monitoring patient</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"add-patient\">\n            <h3>➕ Ajouter un patient</h3>\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"patientName\" placeholder=\"Nom du patient\">\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"patientId\" placeholder=\"ID (ex: patient_001)\">\n                <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" onclick=\"addPatient()\">Ajouter</button>\n            </div>\n            <label>📦 Content Node Code (obligatoire):</label>\n            <input type=\"text\" id=\"contentNodeCode\" placeholder=\"ex: health-data\" value=\"health-data\">\n            <small style=\"color: #666;\">⭐ Code du content node dans Nodify</small>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div id=\"patientsContainer\"></div>\n        \n        <div class=\"log\" id=\"globalLog\">\n            > Système de monitoring santé démarré<br>\n            > Entrez un Content Node Code (ex: health-data)<br>\n            > Ajoutez des patients pour commencer\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\t$content(SCRIPT-1775422952313)\n</body>\n</html>",
