        "type": "STYLE",
        "description": "simulator_health",
        "content": "    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;\n        }\n        .add-patient {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .add-patient h3 {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .form-group {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 10px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n        input, select {\n            padding: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            transition: transform 0.2s;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .btn-primary {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            color: white;\n        }\n        .btn-danger {\n            background: #f44336;\n            color: white;\n        }\n        .btn-success {\n            background: #4caf50;\n            color: white;\n        }\n        .btn-warning {\n            background: #ff9800;\n            color: white;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.02);\n        }\n        .patient-card {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            transition: all 0.3s;\n        }\n        .patient-header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 15px 20px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        .patient-header:hover {\n            opacity: 0.95;\n        }\n        .patient-content {\n            padding: 20px;\n            display: none;\n        }\n        .patient-content.active {\n            display: block;\n        }\n        .vital-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));\n            gap: 15px;\n            margin: 15px 0;\n        }\n        .vital-card {\n            background: #f7f7f7;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .vital-label {\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #666;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n        .vital-value {\n            font-size: 28px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .vital-unit {\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #999;\n        }\n        .status-normal { color: #4caf50; }\n        .status-warning { color: #ff9800; }\n        .status-critical { color: #f44336; }\n        .alert-badge {\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding: 4px 12px;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .alert-normal {\n            background: #4caf50;\n            color: white;\n        }\n        .alert-warning {\n            background: #ff9800;\n            color: white;\n            animation: pulse 1s infinite;\n        }\n        .alert-critical {\n            background: #f44336;\n            color: white;\n            animation: blink 0.5s infinite;\n        }\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n            50% { opacity: 0.7; }\n        }\n        @keyframes blink {\n            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n            50% { opacity: 0.5; }\n        }\n        .button-group {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 10px;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n        .log {\n            background: #2d2d2d;\n            color: #00ff00;\n            padding: 15px;\n            font-family: monospace;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            height: 150px;\n            overflow-y: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .data-info {\n            background: #e3f2fd;\n            padding: 8px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-family: monospace;\n            font-size: 11px;\n            margin: 10px 0;\n            word-break: break-all;\n            display: none;\n        }\n        hr {\n            margin: 15px 0;\n            border: none;\n            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;\n        }\n        label {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            display: block;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n    </style>",
